"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-indian-wrestler-vinesh-phogat-disqualified-weight-paris-olympics-b1175186.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  The Standard's journalism is supported by our readers.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.117806573080811e-33, \"text\": \"The Standard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vinesh Phogat, a female wrestler fromIndia, wasdisqualifiedfrom theParis Olympicson Wednesday (August 7) after failing a weigh-in before thewrestlingfinals.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat, 29, was reportedly only a few kilograms over the 50kg category limit, meaning she could not compete for gold.\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is with regret that the Indian contingent shares news of the disqualification ofVinesh Phogatfrom the women's wrestling 50kg class,\\\" the Indian Olympic Association (IOA) said.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.7568334510555507, \"rank\": 0.3212790857296248, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Indian Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Despite the best efforts by the team through the night, she weighed in a few grams over 50kg this morning.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No further comments will be made by the contingent at this time.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Indian team requests you respect Vinesh's privacy.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1020, \"end\": 1026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.7568334510555507, \"rank\": 0.3212790857296248, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1053, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would like to focus on the competitions on hand.\\\"\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to competition rules, wrestlers must undergo several weigh-ins across multi-day events and usually face disqualification if they fail any.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat had passed an earlier weigh-in.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1275, \"end\": 1281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She then reportedly underwent extreme physical training, including jogging and skipping at night, to shed the extra weight before the next weigh-in.\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coming in at 100g over the limit, her efforts were just shy of the mark and she could not go head-to-head against Team USA's Sarah Hildebrandt as planned.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.7465943749899827, \"rank\": 0.3382268686164378, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1589, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"score\": 0.9999999999718057, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Hildebrandt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to theTimes of India, Phogat is recovering after being hospitalised with dehydration.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An outpouring of sympathy has greeted her disqualification, including a message from Indian Prime MinisterNarendra Modiwho branded her a \\\"champion among champions\\\".\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1802, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.7568334510555507, \"rank\": 0.3212790857296248, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You are India's pride and an inspiration for each and every Indian,\\\" Modi added.\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1892, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9996922467968731, \"rank\": 0.00029989788511956687, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 1944, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.7568334510555507, \"rank\": 0.3212790857296248, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today's setback hurts.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wish words could express the sense of despair that I am experiencing.\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, I know that you epitomise resilience.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has always been your nature to take challenges head on.\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Come back stronger!\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all rooting for you.\\\"\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Others expressed outrage at Phogat's misfortune.\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Journalist Shekhar Gupta said: \\\"Vinesh Phogat disqualification on the verge of a gold & a sealed silver is a national sporting tragedy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2288, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shekhar_Gupta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shekhar Gupta\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shekhar_Gupta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shekhar_Gupta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Shocking failure also by team, contingent bosses & coach.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wrestlers' weight management issues when fighting on consecutive days are well known.\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a management disaster,\\\" Gupta added.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2589, \"end\": 2594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"score\": 0.9969009174995278, \"rank\": 0.0030472771413047935, \"text\": \"Gupta\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gupta_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat is a three-time Olympian from a prominent wrestling family in India.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2603, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}, {\"begin\": 2626, \"end\": 2634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999995688995, \"rank\": 4.3093324826056675e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9996922467968731, \"rank\": 0.00029989788511956687, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is also well known for her role in last year's anti-sexual harassment protests in India.\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9996922467968731, \"rank\": 0.00029989788511956687, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She campaigned for the disbandment of the Wrestling Federation of India (WFI) following harassment allegations made by female athletes.\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat's Olympic disqualification came shortly after another female athlete faced a similar fate due to her weight in another sport.\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 3042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2910, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Youmna Ayyad, an Egyptian boxer, had also initially qualified to compete in this year's Olympics butfailed to passthe criteria in the 54kg category.\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3061, \"end\": 3069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"score\": 0.9501461590000864, \"rank\": 0.052217743322513145, \"text\": \"Egyptian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to her team, the athlete's weight gain was attributed to \\\"physiological and hormonal changes understandable to all women and doctors\\\".\", \"from\": 3194, \"to\": 3338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today's Olympics schedule: Team GB events, Day 12 medal highlights and how to watch the Paris Games  How has this summer of Olympic joy turned into a bonfire of British hate?\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3501, \"end\": 3508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6606883169605909, \"rank\": 0.5120430704826725, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table and latest count today  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  